824
00:46:29,627 --> 00:46:31,561
I'm gonna kill
them little pinheads.

825
00:46:31,595 --> 00:46:33,426
Yeah? Well, you came
to the right place...

826
00:46:33,464 --> 00:46:35,796
because guess who's here...
Derek Lutz.

827
00:46:41,906 --> 00:46:44,431
Hey, Lutz!

828
00:46:44,475 --> 00:46:46,033
You know who I am?

829
00:46:46,076 --> 00:46:47,941
Let me see...

830
00:46:47,978 --> 00:46:50,572
protruding
supra-orbital ridges...

831
00:46:50,614 --> 00:46:54,209
small cranium,
1,300 C.C. Brain...

832
00:46:54,251 --> 00:46:55,445
Neanderthal man.

833
00:46:55,486 --> 00:46:58,546
You... I want you
to call his mother.

834
00:46:58,589 --> 00:47:00,386
You tell her
he's never coming home.

835
00:47:00,424 --> 00:47:03,018
