I'm in and out in two hours.

905
00:50:54,892 --> 00:50:56,291
Oh, Thornton, don't you see?

906
00:50:56,326 --> 00:50:58,123
The reason you want
to read these works...

907
00:50:58,162 --> 00:51:00,096
is so you can experience them
for yourself...

908
00:51:00,130 --> 00:51:02,928
so you can share the thoughts
and feelings of the writer...

909
00:51:02,966 --> 00:51:05,457
without the interference
of your actor and director...

910
00:51:05,502 --> 00:51:07,333
and professor's point of view
getting in the way...

911
00:51:07,371 --> 00:51:10,169
to truly share
and understand...

912
00:51:10,207 --> 00:51:12,107
the common feelings
of all mankind...

913
00:51:12,142 --> 00:51:14,440
the feelings of being alive.

914
00:51:16,046 --> 00:51:18,105
That was beautiful.

915
00:51:18,148 --> 00:51:20,116
I understand
what you're saying, too.

916
00:51:20,150 --> 00:51:21,947
I'm glad.
That makes me feel good.

917
00:51:21,985 --> 00:51:24,283
I got an idea.

918
00:51:24,321 --> 00:51:27,484
Let's keep talking over dinner.

919
00:51:27,524 --> 00:51:29,617
I'm supposed to meet
someone for dinner.

920
00:51:30,827 --> 00:51:33,295
I could cancel,
though, I guess.

921
00:51:33,330 --> 00:51:34,661
We are working, after all.

922
00:51:34,698 --> 00:51:36,529
You can't work
on an empty stomach.

923
00:51:36,567 --> 00:51:39,559
You can't concentrate
when you're hungry.

924
00:51:39,603 --> 00:51:41,571
Oh, I don't know.
I really shouldn't.

925
00:51:41,605 --> 00:51:44,472
- I have so many things to do.
- Oh, come on. I'll help you.

926
00:51:44,508 --> 00:51:46,533
I'll take out the garbage.
I'll do the dishes.

927
00:51:46,577 --> 00:51:48,408
I'll do your nails.
I'll do your hair.

928
00:51:48,445 --> 00:51:50,208
You have no idea
what I want to do.

929
00:51:50,247 --> 00:51:52,215
- I'll call him.
- I'll dial it!

930
00:51:52,249 --> 00:51:54,911
I'll just get the light.

931
00:51:54,952 --> 00:51:57,887
I think I'm attracted
to teachers.

932
00:51:57,921 --> 00:52:00,481
I took out an English teacher.
That didn't work out at all.

933
00:52:00,524 --> 00:52:03,049
I sent her a love letter.
She corrected it.

934
00:52:05,495 --> 00:52:07,622
Oh, great. Company.

935
00:52:11,868 --> 00:52:14,996
- Those two ought to get a room.
- Really.

936
00:52:15,038 --> 00:52:16,505
Actually,
I was married twice.

937
00:52:16,540 --> 00:52:20,203
My first wife, Jason's mother,
I really loved her.

938
00:52:20,244 --> 00:52:22,576
We had a good thing going,
you know?

939
00:52:22,613 --> 00:52:24,808
She passed away
about ten years ago.

940
00:52:24,848 --> 00:52:27,476
After that, I screwed around
for a few years.

941
00:52:27,517 --> 00:52:30,816
Then I really went nuts...
I married Vanessa.

942
00:52:30,854 --> 00:52:32,879
I was just lonely, I guess.

943
00:52:32,923 --> 00:52:34,185
Is that over now?

944
00:52:34,224 --> 00:52:35,919
We were doomed from the start.

945
00:52:35,959 --> 00:52:37,927
I'm an earth sign,
she's a water sign.

946
00:52:37,961 --> 00:52:39,189
Together, we made mud.

947
00:52:39,229 --> 00:52:42,721
I picked a beauty.
And she played around, too.

948
00:52:42,766 --> 00:52:45,428
When she said, "I do,"
I should have said, "With who?"

949
00:52:45,469 --> 00:52:47,869
So, are you
giving up on women?

950
00:52:47,904 --> 00:52:50,202
I don't know.
I can't figure women out.

951
00:52:50,240 --> 00:52:51,537
Today, they're independent.

952
00:52:51,575 --> 00:52:53,440
They only think
about themselves.

953
00:52:53,477 --> 00:52:56,674
During sex, Vanessa used
to scream out her own name.

954
00:52:58,749 --> 00:53:00,216
I think it's the men
who are different.

955
00:53:00,250 --> 00:53:01,512
Ever since
the women's movement...

956
00:53:01,551 --> 00:53:03,143
most of the men I meet
go out of their way...

957
00:53:03,186 --> 00:53:04,915
to show you
how sensitive they are.

958
00:53:04,955 --> 00:53:08,948
Before they were too macho,
and now they're too soft.

959
00:53:08,992 --> 00:53:10,960
You all want us to know
you can cry.

960
00:53:10,994 --> 00:53:14,020
No, with women,
I never cry. Never.

961
00:53:14,064 --> 00:53:15,554
I beg.

962
00:53:19,469 --> 00:53:21,437
If we finish
this bottle of wine...

963
00:53:21,471 --> 00:53:23,769
you won't have to beg.

964
00:53:40,757 --> 00:53:41,917
Diane!

965
00:53:43,827 --> 00:53:45,294
Oh, Philip.

966
00:53:45,329 --> 00:53:47,263
