1426
01:23:14,896 --> 01:23:18,229
"Rage, rage against
the dying of the light.

1427
01:23:18,266 --> 01:23:20,700
"Wild men who caught...

1428
01:23:20,735 --> 01:23:23,761
"and sang the sun in flight
and learned too late...

1429
