"Rage, rage against
the dying of the light.

1435
01:23:43,024 --> 01:23:47,757
"And you, my father,
there on the sad height.

1436
01:23:47,796 --> 01:23:49,821
"Curse, bless me now...

1437
01:23:49,865 --> 01:23:51,799
"with your fierce tears,
I pray.

1438
01:23:51,833 --> 01:23:55,200
"Do not go gentle
into that good night.

1439
01:23:55,237 --> 01:23:59,298
"Rage! Rage against
the dying of the light!"

1440
01:23:59,341 --> 01:24:02,139
Thornton, what does that poem
mean to you?

1441
01:24:02,177 --> 01:24:04,270
It means...

1442
01:24:04,312 --> 01:24:06,610
I don't take shit from no one.

1443
01:24:08,049 --> 01:24:10,040
I'm gonna pass this test.

1444
01:24:10,085 --> 01:24:13,646
I'm stayin' in school!
Who's next?

1445
01:24:16,691 --> 01:24:19,751
Now diving for
the Atlantic Eastern Eagles...

1446
01:24:19,794 --> 01:24:23,753
current conference champion...
Doug Nelson.

1447
01:24:23,798 --> 01:24:26,323
You know what you
almost never see?

1448
01:24:26,368 --> 01:24:29,496
Somebody heckling a diver.

1449
01:24:42,150 --> 01:24:45,142
- You're all right, kid.
- Thanks, Lou.

1450
01:24:45,187 --> 01:24:49,851
Please refrain from making
loud noises during the dives.

1451
01:24:52,027 --> 01:24:55,929
Next up, the Atlantic
Eastern Eagles'...

1452
01:24:55,964 --> 01:24:57,989
Bill Steincap.

1453
01:25:16,484 --> 01:25:20,477
That concludes Atlantic
Eastern's ten-meter dives.

1454
01:25:20,522 --> 01:25:23,320
Next up,
the Grand Lakes Hooters.

1455
01:25:26,261 --> 01:25:27,888
We would like to remind you...

1456
01:25:27,929 --> 01:25:30,193
tickets to all Grand Lakes
sporting events...

1457
01:25:30,232 --> 01:25:33,292
are available through
the student services office.

1458
01:25:33,335 --> 01:25:35,428
Are you interested
in Valerie Desmond?

1459
01:25:35,470 --> 01:25:38,064
She's with me.

1460
01:25:38,106 --> 01:25:40,836
Coming into your own,
are you, Melon?

1461
01:25:40,875 --> 01:25:42,342
I wouldn't break my arm...

1462
01:25:42,377 --> 01:25:44,607
patting myself on the back
if I were you.

1463
01:25:44,646 --> 01:25:46,637
Because... get this, towel boy...

1464
01:25:46,681 --> 01:25:49,809
no matter what you think,
you will always be a crude...

1465
01:25:49,851 --> 01:25:52,479
