just like your father.

1467
01:25:54,889 --> 01:25:58,848
God, I hope so,
'cause I happen to love the guy.

1468
01:25:58,893 --> 01:26:02,192
First up for
Grand Lakes University...

1469
01:26:02,230 --> 01:26:04,357
Chas Osbourne...

1470
01:26:04,399 --> 01:26:07,129
former national
high school champion.

