01:26:34,429 --> 01:26:37,421
- Jason dive yet?
- Not yet. Did you pass?

1472
01:26:37,465 --> 01:26:38,932
I don't know.
They'll let me know.

1473
01:26:38,967 --> 01:26:41,697
Now diving
for Grand Lakes University...

1474
01:26:41,736 --> 01:26:44,068
Jason Melon.

1475
01:27:03,792 --> 01:27:05,817
Attaboy, Jason! You did it!

1476
01:27:11,199 --> 01:27:12,223
All right!

1477
01:27:17,038 --> 01:27:19,506
I can't believe it.
We could actually win this.

1478
01:27:19,541 --> 01:27:23,500
Melon's dive has put the Hooters
back in this meet.

1479
01:27:24,979 --> 01:27:26,446
What's the matter?

1480
01:27:27,982 --> 01:27:29,950
You're up next, Chas.

1481
01:27:32,887 --> 01:27:34,980
I have got
a really bad cramp.

1482
01:27:35,023 --> 01:27:37,321
I've been having
really bad cramps all week.

1483
01:27:37,359 --> 01:27:40,624
- It's probably menstrual.
- Screw you, Melon!

1484
01:27:43,298 --> 01:27:47,257
Coach Turnbull,
you got another eligible diver?

1485
01:27:49,704 --> 01:27:51,171
Melon!

1486
01:27:54,542 --> 01:27:58,842
Melon! We need ya!
Get your suit on!

1487
01:27:58,880 --> 01:28:00,006
Go ahead.

1488
01:28:00,048 --> 01:28:02,175
Oh, not a chance.
In the shape I'm in...

1489
01:28:02,217 --> 01:28:04,310
you could donate my body
to science fiction.

1490
01:28:04,352 --> 01:28:06,718
Get your suit on! We need ya!

1491
01:28:06,755 --> 01:28:10,156
Come on, pal.
Show 'em what you got.

1492
01:28:10,191 --> 01:28:12,489
Melon! We need ya!

1493
01:28:17,432 --> 01:28:22,028
Now diving in substitution
for Grand Lakes University...

1494
01:28:22,070 --> 01:28:24,470
Thornton Melon.

1495
01:28:26,341 --> 01:28:28,571
He's on my substitute roster...

1496
01:28:28,610 --> 01:28:31,135
but I don't have it right now.

1497
01:28:31,179 --> 01:28:34,876
But what I'll do is,
first chance I get...

1498
01:28:34,916 --> 01:28:36,474
I'll bring it to you.

1499
01:28:54,869 --> 01:28:57,303
What dive is he gonna do?

1500
01:28:57,338 --> 01:29:00,273
The Triple Lindy.

1501
01:29:00,308 --> 01:29:02,538
Melon! Melon! Melon!

1502
01:29:09,284 --> 01:29:11,844
There will be an additional
springboard installed...

1503
01:29:11,886 --> 01:29:14,684
for Melon's dive,
the Triple Lindy.

1504
01:29:14,722 --> 01:29:17,282
- Is that hard?
- It's impossible.

1505
01:30:40,842 --> 01:30:43,333
Melon! You did it!

1506
01:30:48,249 --> 01:30:49,614
That was great!

1507
01:30:54,255 --> 01:30:58,214
Oh, you were great!
That was incredible!

1508
01:30:58,259 --> 01:31:00,727
I guess there's nothing
you can't do.

1509
01:31:00,762 --> 01:31:02,923
I've got the results
of your exams right here.

1510
01:31:02,964 --> 01:31:04,090
Do I want to hear 'em?

1511
01:31:04,132 --> 01:31:06,726
You passed!
All "Ds" and an "A."

1512
01:31:06,768 --> 01:31:08,793
Who gave me the "A"?

1513
01:31:08,836 --> 01:31:11,168
- I did.
- Oh, yeah?

1514
01:31:11,205 --> 01:31:13,799
I would like to introduce
our speaker today.

1515
01:31:13,841 --> 01:31:15,274
This is the first time...

1516
01:31:15,310 --> 01:31:18,711
in the history
of this fine institution...

1517
01:31:18,746 --> 01:31:21,579
that a freshman
has given this address.

1518
01:31:21,616 --> 01:31:24,210
Mr. Thornton Melon.

1519
01:31:37,198 --> 01:31:38,358
Thank you very much.

1520
01:31:38,399 --> 01:31:41,163
Thank you, Dean Martin,
President Sinclair...

1521
01:31:41,202 --> 01:31:43,670
and members
of the graduating class.

1522
01:31:43,705 --> 01:31:46,538
I have only one thing
to say to you today...

1523
01:31:46,574 --> 01:31:48,007
it's a jungle out there.

1524
01:31:48,042 --> 01:31:50,602
You gotta look out
for number one.

1525
01:31:50,645 --> 01:31:53,443
But don't step in number two.

1526
01:31:54,949 --> 01:31:57,975
And so,
to all you graduates...

1527
01:31:58,019 --> 01:32:02,115
as you go out into the world
my advice to you is...

1528
01:32:02,156 --> 01:32:05,125
don't go!
It's rough out there.

1529
01:32:05,159 --> 01:32:08,128
Move back with your parents.
Let them worry about it.

